"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-10-Can-China-achieve-perfect-ends-in-diving-table-tennis-at-Paris-2024--1vX24G4pzlC-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  Olympians from around the world are competing in 39 gold medal events at the 2024 Paris Summer Games on Saturday.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 340, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chinese athletes have so far won all of the table tennis titles in the French capital, and will face Japan in the women's team final at South Paris Arena 4 at 15:00 (GMT+2), looking to secure the country's fifth gold in the sport and extend their winning streak on the female side to five in a row.\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 342, \"end\": 349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.728865625026603, \"rank\": 0.32166598665015783, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 413, \"end\": 419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.891229003877038, \"rank\": 0.11091769509378595, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 443, \"end\": 448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 0.7143726755247656, \"rank\": 0.39429109388048367, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_baseball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the same time at the Paris Aquatic Centre, China's Cao Yuan and Yang Hao will both take part in the men's 10-meter platform diving final.\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 666, \"end\": 671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999946317075, \"rank\": 5.368393432455872e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 696, \"end\": 704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cao_Yuan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cao Yuan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cao_Yuan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cao_Yuan\"}, {\"begin\": 709, \"end\": 717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yang_Hao_(Sui_dynasty)\", \"score\": 0.5916864370255184, \"rank\": 0.40495867768596194, \"text\": \"Yang Hao\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yang_Hao_(Sui_dynasty)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yang_Hao_(Sui_dynasty)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If either contender finishes on top of the podium, their delegation will complete a sweep of all eight golds in the sport.\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chinese boxer Li Qian will meet Atheyna Bylon of Panama in the women's 75-kilogram final at Roland Garros Stadium at 22:34 (GMT+2).\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 1038, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 907, \"end\": 914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.728865625026603, \"rank\": 0.32166598665015783, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 939, \"end\": 952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atheyna_Bylon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Atheyna Bylon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atheyna_Bylon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atheyna_Bylon\"}, {\"begin\": 956, \"end\": 962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panama\", \"score\": 0.9999480365665943, \"rank\": 4.281207572219868e-05, \"text\": \"Panama\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panama\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the USA will seek to extend its dominance in Olympic men's basketball, while host nation France looks to stand in the way and spring an upset in the final at Bercy Arena at 21:30 (GMT+2).\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1231, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1048, \"end\": 1051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7813339683319397, \"rank\": 0.2766611464163594, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1133, \"end\": 1139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.614515684556044, \"rank\": 0.6114369706382706, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1493, \"entities\": []}]}"